ASSIGNMENT #8 (Group):  Cost, Quality and Risk Management   due March 1
	 
	From your WBS and Gantt Chart, estimate how much this project would cost if you were employed.  Use figures presented in class.
	 
	State in 1-2 paragraphs how you would control for quality.  What measurements would you take in order to make a case that this project was of high quality?
	 
	List the risks involved in doing this project at each step.  Accompany each with a statement about how you would mitigate risk.
	 
	Name the file TEAMNAMECost and submit it by putting it in the Google Docs folder you have permitted to us.

In order to calculate costs, aside from the real cost of renting the consoles and TVs, we did some research on what would be an average salary for an Event Coordinator which is basically the work we are doing in this project. To do so we completed a simple survey in http://www.payscale.com/ that matched our skills with a typical hourly rate. Getting the actual cost would be a matter of multiplying this by the number of hours we stated we would work in the Business Case.
